          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-[#1a1a1a] to-[#111111] border border-[#333333] p-6 rounded-sm"><h3 class="text-[#00ffff] font-mono text-xl uppercase tracking-wide">ğŸ“Š Tracker PostÄ™pÃ³w</h3></div>
